---
title: Thai Spiced Whiting with a Noodle and Cabbage Stir-Fry
description: Fragrant and nourishing, our 20-minute Thai spiced whiting is a deliciously healthy recipe for busy evenings. Whiting, sourced from our suppliers in Cornwall, is a light tasting white fish with a similar meaty texture to cod making it a versatile ingredient to use in dishes like this one.  Rubbed in our specially blended Thai spice (a fragrant mix of spices like ground coriander, green peppercorns, lemongrass and sesame seeds) and pan-fried to form a lovely crust, we’ve served the whiting with a cabbage and noodle stir fry and finished off the dish with crunchy peanuts for an added layer of texture.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-spiced-tilapia-ea32bfe5-312c5c9e.jpg
